- Smart Notifications: Stay updated with real-time email notifications for approvals, submissions, and policy violations.
- Secure and Compliant: Fyle prioritizes your data security and ensures compliance with global security regulations like SOC2 Type I and Type II, PCI DSS & GDPR.
